Explicitly stating the goal is "Resume / Portfolio" justifies complexity.\
* **Context:** Setting up a Postgres Datamart for a beer league might seem like overkill, but as a demonstration of "End-to-End Data Engineering," it is perfect. It turns potential "over-engineering" into a feature.\
